      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6 August 1884. ¶  ¶ Enclosed I am sending you, esteemed Mr Holtze, fresh seeds of  ¶ Castilloa elastica ¶ , ¶  one of the best caoutchouc (India rubber) trees. I have just received these seeds directl...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">84.08.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Maurice Holtze</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">GRG 19/391, State Records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">6/8/84</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hierbei sende ich Ihnen, geehrter Herr Holtze, frische Samen von <name key="Castilloa%20elastica">Castilloa elastica</name>, einem der besten Caoutchouc (India Rubber) Bäume. Ich habe diese Samen eben </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">direct</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> aus </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Mexico</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> erhalten.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe neuen bot. </seg>Sendungen aus Ihrer doch noch unvollständig erforschten Flora entgegen gesehen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ganz der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Bitte Meer Algen (Seaweeds) u Meer Gräser (Seagrasses) dort nicht unbeachtet zu lassen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Besten Gruss an Hr Foelsche.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6 August 1884.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed I am sending you, esteemed Mr Holtze, fresh seeds of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Castilloa%20elastica">Castilloa elastica</name>
               </seg>,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The name is spelled in this way in a number of contemporary sources, for example in J. Hooker (1884c), but is more usually written <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Castilla</seg>.</p>
               </note> one of the best caoutchouc (India rubber) trees. I have just received these seeds directly from Mexico.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have been looking forward to new botanical dispatches from your after all only incompletely explored flora. </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Please do not disregard marine algae (seaweeds) and marine grasses (seagrasses) there.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Best regards to Mr Foelsche.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Castilloa%20elastica">Castilloa elastica</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
